cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.CC 

The paper focuses on machine learning and intelligence, which are core topics in computer science. The use of physics and information theory in the research suggests that it may fall under the categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.IT (Information Theory). The exploration of causality and the development of a robust algorithm for classification with noisy labels suggest that it may also fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
